    "created_at": "2016-07-29T06:38:32Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-07-29T06:38:32Z",
    "body": "This is the classic problem when subscribing to an event of and object in the main process, the `WebContents` is not destroyed when you refresh the page, and the remote callback is not cleaned.\n\nYou probably need to use DOM's `contextmenu` event instead, or refactor the module to send IPC messages to the page for the `context-menu` event.\n"
  },
